{"tid":2413823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇一個地方是必須用安心出行","createTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T02:43:14.000Z","uid":73092,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f64ac5078f98c5291f3a2e986f54c0fed858f66","tid":2413823,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"冇一個地方是必須用安心出行（可以選填資料）！<br />\n所以用鬼機裝，不了！假App，不了！<br />\n好多黃店守得咁辛苦，有啲花人手時間整登記表，有啲索性唔開晚市，我哋都盡一分力，唔好令人誤以為多人用安心出行。<br />\n安心出行不單是私隱問題，而且是大規模監控的雛形，希望香港人真係可以守住，總之就「唔裝」！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GoldwaterFellows/posts/502102264523142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGoldwaterFellows%2Fposts%2F502102264523142&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69IlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=388e17ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GoldwaterFellows/posts/502102264523142</a>"},{"pid":"4e6b4bf6f66711b3de370c3bc0138dc96409f7bf","tid":2413823,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b99a2807cc3d8423ee936e6fdea526f5bd82135","tid":2413823,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9774965e6018081a9a8b4921eef543bbf5bc319b","tid":2413823,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"780138e25257cb2b31a4788b58481482a9a10e97","tid":2413823,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4705f2d8e3f317d7c87010ad3b1224de62390c45","tid":2413823,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d886164e75aefd7522c5541269573c224b3ce2e0","tid":2413823,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/